Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:09.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ryugamine...Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:12.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's really you, Kida?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gang activity has been declining recently, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They got into a fight with some Saitama\N guys and a bunch of people got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:22.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sonohara Anri. I hope the year goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:23.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:29.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You pledged to become a fine Ikebukuroer,\N so show us all and overcome this tribulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, my...love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it back! I'll give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I made you take that ridiculous job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:56.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've finished it without any problems;\N it's because that thing showed up randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not human. You're a monster! A monster! A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard a voice coming from your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It called me a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:23.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a rude jerk. It should've at least called you an enchantress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it's an alien?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:51.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is apparently comprised of jokes, caprices, and coincidences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.79,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:56.50,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.13,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The strong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:57.75,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.17,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:58.59,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans who love and hope
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:58.96,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Because hope is strong people human love. Because because because hope is is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.21,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:03:59.42,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,am I, so I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:03:59.63,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:03:59.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong, people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:00.13,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.42,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I, love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:00.71,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:05.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation may also be one of God's jokes or caprices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:09.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are thirty-seven girls I've fallen in love with at first sight since entering high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:16.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And like a plot twist in a drama, I get to walk home from school \Nwith one of my top five, who happens to be this girl with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this country bumpkin is getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been pretty tough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally surprised back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you ran away without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I wouldn't have passed up a chance like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:53.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now we'd be in West Gate Park voicing our love to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And on that note, please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai—, Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are currently seven girls I'm waiting to hear from,\N and I'm still deciding which one I'll actually date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to take him seriously, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just tire you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:14.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes it sound like he's toying with you, but \Nit's no big deal. Even if he hits on you, ultimately—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:22.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's my best friend, Ryugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a country bumpkin who's only been in Ikebukuro for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:31.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's unsophisticated and naïve, he's \Noddly stubborn and someone you just can't leave alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm somehow involved in a love triangle with this pure boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call "youth?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurt—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.94,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...quite friendly with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to be, but we're inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, uncle, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To explain how this all came to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to retrace our steps back to the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yagiri Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the year goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Yagiri, you can sit down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:10.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be coming to school for a while—no, I might not ever come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:15.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to waste with the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:23.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri, wait. I said, "Wait!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of different types of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.55,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so Mikado tells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be what it's like to fall in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.80,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri, isn't there something—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest throbs just by having her smile at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:35.78,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.54,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu-But...being absent on your first day of school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess she wasn't smiling, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:55.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's the day I immediately updated the \Nnumber one ranked girl on my list of possible girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You on your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:12.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sonohara, something's bugging you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:16.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're being bullied or you're involved in some trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:17.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If something ever happens, tell me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Harima still hasn't come to school yet, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:30.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you two are in the same class...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:35.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard to get you two in the same class, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:40.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Saitou from your middle school also insisted that you two be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:43.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have to hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, how about I take you home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:51.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You do know that The Slasher appeared in Ikebukuro again, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Nasujima, are you sexually harassing her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:01.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, making our glasses-wearing class rep scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:05.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that full-on sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it more like sexy embarrassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon now, Kida, stop goofing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara, you wouldn't misunderstand and start weird rumors, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she look like the frivolous kind of woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I'll leave her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:24.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be the one spreading rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this make me a crusader of justice for the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.26,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so cool just now, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would fall for me after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida? And Sonohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you have come at a worse time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:09:00.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the rumors about Nasujima are mostly just \Nthat, but it is true he's laid his hands on a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:00.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:06.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A second-year student named Niekawa Haruna transferred out during the second term.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:10.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the reason was that people\N would find out she was dating Nasujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows whether she wanted to transfer, whether \NNasujima threatened her into it, or if the school forced her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if something happens to you,\N Mikado and I will do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:28.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't totally grasp the situation, but I'll do whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:33.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. This is where you're supposed to say, "I might not \Nbe able to do it, but I'll be able to with the power of love!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a man if you don't say something to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Isn't that a contradiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, about before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:41.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls who were bullying you were from your middle school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, listening to your conversation, I figured they had to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:56.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a, "you were saved by a good person, but now that she's disappeared they've come back," kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:01.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Your friend's disappeared? And no one's found her yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Harima Mika from our class, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:14.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika's just marked as absent at school, but she \Nhasn't been home since before opening ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally something you should tell the police about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:21.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She contacted my cell phone and Harima's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:25.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "I'm going on a trip to heal my broken heart. Don't worry."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A trip to heal her broken heart? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...will you promise to listen without freaking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised by much anymore\N after what's happened these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima...is a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:46.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you were asking that guy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:51.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika went on her broken-heart trip after being\N dumped by the guy she was stalking—er, courting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't do anything but leave it to her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:59.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she still doesn't come back, all we can do is call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she a close friend to you, Sonohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the interrogative?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess his intuition is good with some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awkward with a lot of things and not very good at \Ndealing with people, but Mika would always pull me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt bad that she even chose the same high school as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:35.96,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you think Mika didn't want to let go of her because she \Nwas using her to stand out, you shouldn't actually say that, Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:36.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That she was just using me to look cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I used her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that life would be easier, that\N I couldn't live without depending on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I don't think it's that important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:12:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've adjusted...to living without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:09.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I became a class rep because she wanted to, \Nso I figured I should at least do it in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like if I became a class rep, then I could surpass her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of like cheating though, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my opinion, what's cheating is telling people all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:25.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're trying to get someone to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to surpass Harima is the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:34.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should hold your head high and be more confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:48.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like about this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lame," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The strongest in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You from some magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya mean by "strongest?" That's too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about the strongest person in Ikebukuro, it's gotta be that black biker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:13.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about The Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd hafta say the strongest group here is The Dollars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, The Dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:26.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I go a different way from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye, Anri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:36.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought of this before, but maybe\N we'd find that Mika girl with Yagiri after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like a stalker and her victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she abducted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People are missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are we going to look for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave them be. She said not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:51.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only an organized group would be able to pull this off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like The Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of joining The Dollars, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? No. No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People only join gangs when they're young and impressionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, most people regret joining them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...yeah, but we're still young and impressionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:11.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:17.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was extremely depressed before Mikado came to Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:22.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to make it through the day thanks to lots of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also thanks to Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:30.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's new to Ikebukuro and still vulnerable to the sweltering atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's new, he's more likely to get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.52,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?! It can't sell much worse than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can douse him with cold water, but when I look into his gleaming eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know not even that will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:43.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I try to be with him as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:49.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to get near the darkness this city holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:54.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:03.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself I'd never...go there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika has entered the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.87,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.91,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong, Love, Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I, want, to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.16,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I, want, stronger, love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:36.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong, person, to love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.04,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope, me, mother, mother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.91,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.41,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.71,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Could someone be spamming us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.04,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.25,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.58,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.37,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the kanji for mother is "haha," so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.47,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not afraid it's an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.59,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TsumiUta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's "Zaika."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zaika" as in "property?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Celty, I have a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Mr. Shiki of the Awakusu Association again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that great a job, but will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:12.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another courier job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a courier job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, you have to start by getting the merchandise back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:22.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the merchandise is, or I \Nshould say it was a "don't ask, don't tell" situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:28.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now about the item. The guy who stole it is running around somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where most of the hiding spots are,\N so you should be able to corner him easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:42.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful; that Slasher's been out and about lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:47.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, The Slasher. He appeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He just leaves after inflicting wounds, but never kills anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can't call him the strongest, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest person in this city's gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon from Russia Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:17:00.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That information guy moved over to Shinjuku, but what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihara Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heiwajima Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Color Gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays it's The Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But The Dollars don't have a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:17.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That yellow gang held the most sway until last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:18.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're called The Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:26.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they had an insane brawl with \NThe Blue Squares and lots of people got taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:29.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard they're back in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:33.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, keep the orders coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:37.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have Engawa scallops. They're cheap, they're cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.48,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, don't you see them a lot these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys in yellow, right? So you did notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow? You mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:44.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mellow Scars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean The Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hermes' line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:53.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They should've been eradicated after that battle with The Blue Squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:58.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their boss supposedly left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:18:00.55,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me over any time. Ah, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please tell me about The Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:08.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend's thinking of joining them, but I want to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you asking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't ask anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't want to ask Orihara Izaya anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:28.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we know much about The Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:31.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you everything we do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:36.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes...this city can almost swallow you whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:40.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I won't let you go that far, Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell just by lookin' that we be Yellow Scarves, can'tchya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:11.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...Harima Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:19.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but don't interfere with our flight of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Flight of love...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys really in The Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you because I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Mikado, why you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:08.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.93,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I might be the one who's dependent upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:51.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After Mikado came here, I feel like my bravado's turned into real courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might just be able to face her without running away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The more she expects me to, the more like I'll be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd ever come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:10.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your boyfriend been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He visits me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he did just before now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, did you make sure to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.28,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I banned the spammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.07,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it can be peaceful again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:54.74,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if that were so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:59.24,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I heard that members of The Yellow Scarves got slashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:01.13,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,What are The Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.46,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe The Slasher is working for The Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.00,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:07.05,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,A war might break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:12.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The events which occur in this city may\N seem completely unrelated upon first glance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they definitely connect at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:19.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And probably hold some twisted knowledge that we can't even fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.94,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kida.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:20.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:27.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sonohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:33.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just noticed it, but this relationship feels pretty comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.20,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Points will connect with each other eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if something we can't say right now gets exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:44.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that our relationship will stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:16.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:18.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:23.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll tell you everything about the already-famous Kaztano Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Run Around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:29.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, don't call me Dotachin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.04,0:24:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
